This project is a from-scratch Go implementation of the Symphony specification.
It is not a port or fork of the reference Elixir implementation.

This project implements the Symphony Service Specification (SPEC.md), which is
part of the Symphony project by OpenAI:

  Symphony - https://github.com/openai/symphony
  Copyright 2025 OpenAI
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

The specification (SPEC.md) was used as the design reference for this
implementation. No source code was copied from the original project.
